Class PeronaMalikAnisotropicDiffusion

  • java.lang.Object
    • Catalano.Imaging.Filters.PeronaMalikAnisotropicDiffusion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class PeronaMalikAnisotropicDiffusion
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBaseInPlace
    Perona-Malik Anisotropic diffusion.

    Is a technique aiming at reducing image noise without removing significant parts of the image content, typically edges, lines or other details that are important for the interpretation of the image.

    Author:
    Diego Catalano
